column4: <content>1 zw/w foto Dr. Perman Coll. Sotheby's, verso: copies cf. a group of similar houses in Patinir, Rest on the Flight, Berlin, Dahlem (Koch, fig. 40). One of the Errrera Masters?</content>

<related_object.title>1 zw/w foto Dr. Perman Coll. to be sold 1975, recto: Top drawing cf. Q. Massijs background of Joachim & Angel in Altarpiece of St. Anne, Brussels, Boon repr. p.12; Brown ink mainly, but Gate House in centre and buildings to left & right of bottom fortress in purple ink. One of the Errera Masters? Master of the Half-Lengths or copied from him see Rock Patinir, figs. 73, 74, 81, 83</related_object.title>
